Many of Christie's stories first appeared in journals, newspapers and magazines.{{sfn|Fitzgibbon|1980|p=83}} This list consists of the published collections of stories, in chronological order by UK publication date, even when the book was published first in the US or serialised in a magazine in advance of publication in book form.

